data.description: In The Heart of HOT Historic OAKLAND CITY/WESTMONT NEIGHBORHOOD! Less than 1 mile to ATLANTA'S WESTSIDE BELTLINE trail. This adorable bungalow home is perfect for first-time home buyers or investors looking to add to their portfolio. Home is nestled on a LARGE level lot, perfect for kids, pets and entertaining. Features 3 Bedrooms, 1 renovated Full Bathroom, separate dining room and bonus sitting room or office. The peaceful backyard features a large wooden deck overlooking a private fenced in backyard, great for summer time grilling & gatherings. You can't beat the location, just a few short minutes to Monday Night Brewery, Lee & White Development, Mercedes Benz Stadium, Tyler PerryCOs Studio & right down the street from the famous "Madea House", yet nestled on a quiet street allowing you to get away from it all. Being sold "as is".
